Cell["\<\
Here, you may wish to change the color scheme for graph edges or vertex \
labels. \[LineSeparator]In particular, if you use the dark mode of the \
computer screen, you may turn \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]black\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] to \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]white\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] or vice versa.  \
\>", "Text",
